DISCRETIONARY APPEALS ALLOWED

96-2641. In re Hitchcock.

Cuyahoga App. Nos. 69291 and 69292. (Appeal of Joanne Canitia Brady on behalf of Shampail and Hastings Hitchcock; and appeal of Abdul and Mary Abdullah.) The appeals are allowed and the *1456motion to vacate stay of proceedings is denied.

Resnick and Cook, JJ., dissent.
